---
import { TextSection } from '@components/odyssey-theme';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Page.astro';
import HeroSection from '../../components/sections/heros/HeroSection.astro';

const seo = {
	title: 'About Excaliat',
	description: 'About Excaliat, A well-formed and well organized organization excelling and providing the Cyber Security R&D',
};
---

<Layout {seo}>
	<HeroSection>
		<div slot="text-container">
			<h1>About Excaliat</h1>
			<p>
				Excaliat is a pioneering force in the tech industry, offering custom software and cybersecurity solutions designed to propel businesses into the future. With a global outlook, we deliver innovative products and services worldwide, ensuring each solution meets the unique needs of our clients. Our expertise spans comprehensive software development, consultancy, and technical support, guiding clients through the digital landscape. At DAR, we pride ourselves on setting new industry standards and driving technological advancement. Join us and let's build the future together.
			</p>
		</div>
    <picture slot="image-container">
      <img
        src="/assets/images/home/classic-hero.jpg"
        alt="Astro Odyssee"
        id="home-hero-image"
      />
    </picture>
	</HeroSection>
  <TextSection narrow>
   <h3>Mission</h3>
   <p>At Excaliat, we aim to be the shield in the digital realm, providing cutting-edge cybersecurity and software solutions. Our commitment is to keep your data safe and your operations seamless.
 
    Excaliat stands at the forefront of innovation, crafting software and cybersecurity defenses that protect and empower. We navigate the complexities of the digital world so you can focus on what you do best.
     
    In an era where digital threats loom large, Excaliat serves as the guardian of your digital frontier. We deliver bespoke cybersecurity and software solutions, ensuring peace of mind in a connected world.
     
    Excaliat is where technology meets trust, offering comprehensive cybersecurity and software solutions. We're dedicated to securing your digital landscape, enabling you to build and grow without boundaries.</p>
  </TextSection>
</Layout>
